{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Exempt personal care services from VAT",
        "additional_details": "We seek VAT exemption for personal care services to bolster the struggling sector, enhance affordability, and facilitate accessibility. Additionally, it aligns with the urgent need to address the mental health crisis, given the significant impact these services can have on mental well-being.\r\n \r\nRemoving VAT should support businesses, benefit the economy, and we believe will improve overall mental health outcomes for citizens, ultimately fostering a healthier and more prosperous society.\r\n",
        "background": "We strongly implore the Government to grant VAT exemption for personal care services, such as hairdressing, holistic therapies and beauty therapies. This would help bolster businesses, increase affordability and accessibility, and we believe could help combat the mental health crisis.",
